Where can we find more information on Pelican Bay Lumber Co,?  My wife found a wooden Christmas box that was made by P.B.L.C., and in it was a very old letter entitled,&quot;With Our Compliments, Shipping Containers And Twine For Cheering And Useful Things.&quot;  The letter then begins to say,&quot;To be used by relatives and very close friends of our men in the service from our district.&quot;

It has foreign and domestic shipping rates with very specific instructions about shipping, addressing, and appearance.  We would love more information about this!

Thank you, The Villanueva's
